mapper.insert: insert ignore into uac_user(id, del, creator, create_time, editor, edit_time, username, sys_admin, auth_type, password, nickname, employee_id, department, real_name, avatar, email, mobile) values (#{id}, #{del}, #{creator}, #{createTime}, #{editor}, #{editTime}, #{username}, #{sysAdmin}, #{authType}, #{password}, #{nickname}, #{employeeId}, #{department}, #{realName}, #{avatar}, #{email}, #{mobile})
